  "body": "When going quickly through pages on mobile, it'd be really nice if as you scroll down long menus e.g. in docs, if after navigating to the next page and then returning to the menu if the previous scroll position is maintained/restored.\r\n\r\nThis could be done by a) rendering the menu in the layout component which isnt unmounted on page changes or by storing the menu scroll position in the layout again and then passing it into the page component on render.",
